pro_course_detail.description:
Making your first steps in Russian spoken language 🇷🇺  🇷🇺  🇷🇺
Here we might discuss some basic topics like 
- small talk;
- dos and don'ts in Russia;
- what to do if Russians around you do not drink vodka as was expected;
- Matryoshka, Balalaika, and why Lenin is still on the Red Square

 and much more. 

No matter where your interests lie, we'll find a way to fulfill them!
